OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781712674
OL,3,CWelsh Government promises 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous' childcare in UK with new
OL,5,C#55m boost
OL,7,FHundreds more families across Wales
OL,8,Fwill soon be able to access funded
OL,9,Fchildcare following a #55 million
OL,10,Finvestment announced by the Welsh
OL,11,FGovernment.
OL,13,FThe funding boost, which forms part of
OL,14,Fthe First Supplementary Budget for
OL,15,F2026-27, is aimed at accelerating the
OL,16,Frollout of 12.5 hours of funded
OL,17,Fchildcare per week to all two-year-
OL,18,Folds.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
