OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781712674
OL,3,CWelsh Government promises 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous' childcare in UK with new
OL,5,C#55m boost
OL,7,FWrexham has become the latest local
OL,8,Fauthority to expand the offer to all
OL,9,Ftwo-year-olds in its area, joining
OL,10,FSwansea, Merthyr Tydfil, and Newport.
OL,12,FMinisters say the phased rollout is
OL,13,Fpart of a wider commitment to
OL,14,Feventually provide 20 hours of funded
OL,15,Fcare per week for all children aged
OL,16,Fbetween nine months and four years old.
OL,18,FOnce fully implemented, the Welsh
OL,19,FGovernment claims the scheme will be
OL,20,Fthe "most generous" childcare offer
OL,21,Fanywhere in the UK.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
