PN,43303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781712674
OL,3,CWelsh Government promises 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous' childcare in UK with new
OL,5,C#55m boost
OL,7,FOf the total funding package, #10
OL,8,Fmillion has been earmarked for capital
OL,9,Finvestment to enhance and expand
OL,10,Fexisting childcare settings, with a
OL,11,Ffocus on improving quality, capacity,
OL,12,Fand accessibility.
OL,14,FThe government also hopes the cash
OL,15,Finjection will help prop up providers
OL,16,Ffacing rising demand, strengthen long-
OL,17,Fterm sustainability, and boost Welsh-
OL,18,Fmedium childcare as part of its target
OL,19,Fto reach one million Welsh speakers by
OL,20,F2050.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
