PN,43304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781712674
OL,3,CWelsh Government promises 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous' childcare in UK with new
OL,5,C#55m boost
OL,7,FDeputy First Minister Sioned Williams,
OL,8,Fwho holds responsibility for
OL,9,Fchildcare, said the investment shows
OL,10,Fthe government is "accelerating" its
OL,11,Fcommitments to families.
OL,13,F"Childcare costs in Wales are the
OL,14,Fhighest in the UK and I am determined
OL,15,Fto help families all over Wales, while
OL,16,Falso supporting children's
OL,17,Fdevelopment," she said.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
