PN,43305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F433A1781712674
OL,3,CWelsh Government promises 'most
OL,4,Cgenerous' childcare in UK with new
OL,5,C#55m boost
OL,7,F"I'm particularly pleased that Wrexham
OL,8,Fis now expanding its childcare offer
OL,9,Fto all two-year-olds, and we will
OL,10,Fcontinue to work closely with local
OL,11,Fauthorities across Wales to roll this
OL,12,Fout everywhere. This is spending with
OL,13,Fpurpose, with every pound working
OL,14,Fharder for Wales."
OL,16,FAn Expert Steering Group has been set
OL,17,Fup to advise on the next phases of the
OL,18,Frollout, looking closely at workforce
OL,19,Fplanning, digital applications, and
OL,20,Fmaking sure the system is accessible
OL,21,Ffor all families.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
